the fate of humanity in his hands.</span></div></div></div><div class=""></div></div></div><div data-testid="genresList" class="BookPageMetadataSection__genres"><ul class="CollapsableList" aria-label="Top genres for this book"><span tabindex="-1"><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genrePlainText"><span class="Text Text__body3 Text__subdued">Genres</span></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/science-fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Science Fiction</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fiction" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fiction</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/fantasy" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Fantasy</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/space-opera" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Space Opera</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/science-fiction-fantasy" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Science Fiction Fantasy</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/audiobook" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Audiobook</span></a></span><span class="BookPageMetadataSection__genreButton"><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/genres/horror" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button--small"><span class="Button__labelItem">Horror</span></a></span></span><span tabindex="-1"></span> <div class="Button__container"><button type="button" class="Button Button--tag-inline Button